ICrudRepository<T,TID> Methods

Methods
 NameDescription
Count

Represents method Count.

Delete(IEnumerable)

Overloaded. Removes entities from the database.

Delete(T)

Overloaded. Removes model from the database.

DeleteAll

Deletes all entities managed by the repository.

Exists(TID)

Checks if entity exists in the repository.

FindAll

Retrieves all models from PODO database table.

FindOne(TID)

Retrieves single model from the database based on its primary key value. If record not found, nil is returned.

Insert(IEnumerable)

Overloaded. Inserts models to the database.

Insert(T)

Overloaded. Inserts model to the database .

Save(IEnumerable)

Overloaded. Saves entities to the database. It will do update or the insert based on the entity state.

Save(T)

Overloaded. Saves the entity to the database. It will do update or the insert based on the entity state.

SaveCascade(T)

Saves the entity and all entities it contains to the database. It will do update or the insert based on the entity state.
